# Note: GoogleService-Info.plist is intentionally NOT ignored.
# It has to travel through this repo to reach the Mac, and Firebase iOS config
# values are shipped inside every App Store binary anyway - they are identifiers,
# not secrets. Access is controlled by Firestore/RTDB security rules, not by
# hiding this file. Do not rely on it being private.
